snippet.title: Big Win Soccer Launch Trailer (Google Play)
snippet.description:
Now available for FREE on the Google Play Store for Android!
https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.hotheadgames.google.free.bigwinsoccer

Welcome to world class football fun with Big Win Soccer! No matter what you call the "beautiful game", Big Win Soccer is the game for everyone. 

CREATE your own unique dream team, COMPETE against opponents from around the world, WATCH your team battle it out on the pitch, BOOST your player's passing, shooting, dribbling and other skills and get ready to hoist the Daily Trophy for the ultimate BIG WIN! 

HIGHLIGHTS 
★ Full team and player customisation allowing you to create your own fantasy team! 
★ Open Bronze, Silver and Gold card packs to find new players, skill boosts to improve your team and collect other cards to stay at the top of the table 
★ Play match-changing Big Impact cards and watch them affect the outcome when they come to life as the exciting match action unfolds! 
★ Earn coins and Big Bucks by playing matches, leveling up and winning the Daily Trophy so you can open more card packs 

BIG IMPACT CARDS 
★ Super Strike 
★ Crunching Tackles 
★ Brilliant Delivery 
★ Great Ball 
★ Free Kick Focus 
★ Off The Woodwork 
★ On Target 
★ Nerves of Steel 
★ Penalty Power 
★ Injury Free 
★ and many more...
